high_descs: Turn around towards the bar of soap on the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub basin, to the left of the red cloth.
Pick up the bar of soap on the counter of the bath tub.
Put that bar of soap into the bath tub basin, to the left of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap into a bath tub basin.

high_descs: Turn around and take a small step to your left.
Pick up the pink bar of soap that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the tub then take a big step left.
Put the bar of soap in the tub to the left of the red cloth.
Pick up the bar of soap that's on the lip of the tub in front of you.
Put this bar of soap to the left of the bar of soap you just put in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the soap up from the sink.
Cross the room to face the tub.
Put the soap in the tub.
Pick the soap on the side of the tub up.
Put the bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in a tub.
